<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <link rel="icon" href="public/images/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>SnapSec Demo Account Credentials</title>
</head>

<body style="background: #f0f9ff; margin: 20px; padding: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #334155;">
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 619px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #e0f2fe; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08); color: #334155; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 30px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;">
                <img src="https://snapsec.co/logos/blue-medium.png" alt="SnapSec Logo" style="width: 70px;">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <h1
                    style="text-align: center; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                    Welcome to the Future of Security</h1>
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 10px;">Your SnapSec Demo
                    Account is Ready</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div
                    style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e293b; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hi <strong
                            style="color: #0ea5e9;">{{name}}</strong>,</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #475569; margin: 0;">
                        We're excited to have you explore SnapSec. Use the credentials below to access our full-featured
                        demo environment and see how we can transform your security posture.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);">
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                                        <p
                                            style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e0f2fe; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
                                            Demo Email</p>
                                        <p
                                            style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500;">
                                            {{demo_email}}</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <p
                                            style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e0f2fe; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
                                            Password</p>
                                        <p
                                            style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500; font-family: monospace;">
                                            {{demo_password}}</p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 0;">
                <a href="{{demo_url}}"
                    style="background-color: #0f172a; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block; padding: 18px 45px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2); transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                    Access Demo Dashboard
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div
                    style="background: #fffbeb; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                    <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #92400e; margin: 0;">
                        <strong style="color: #78350f;">💡 Pro Tip:</strong> These credentials are valid for the shared
                        demo environment. Any data you create may be visible to other demo users. For a private POC,
                        contact our sales team.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="font-size: 13px; text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 20px;">
                    If you have any questions or need assistance, our team is here to help.<br>
                    Reply to this email or visit our <a href="https://snapsec.co/support"
                        style="color: #0ea5e9; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Support Center</a>.
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table align="center" style="width: 100%; max-width: 619px; margin: 30px auto; text-align: center;">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
                    &copy; 2026 SnapSec Inc. All rights reserved.<br>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>